# Project Memory Bank Rules

- Keep the memory bank in `memory-bank/`.
- Update the memory bank after material changes, decisions, or new features.
- Record active tasks in `memory-bank/activeContext.md`.
- Record architecture/structure in `memory-bank/systemPatterns.md`.
- Record stack/tooling in `memory-bank/techContext.md`.
- Record progress and done items in `memory-bank/progress.md`.
